race.comment: The strong early pace will suit the top couple of chances. KATHY'S ROSE (2) has had two runs for the new yard, immediately off the mark fresh before a fast finishing third last time. This suits and will be motoring late. RED BEAUTY (8) is another that will be suited by the tempo. Hit the line fresh-up from a break and fitter can run into the finish again. SARAQAEL (5) is an untapped local building a good record. Resuming and did win only other try fresh. Can measure up again. COBBO (3) is better than latest and looks one of the speed influences. Probably has to go forward from the outside but has a nice weight and can give a sight with the blinkers added. GILBERT'S GOLD (4) is overdue for a win and drawn for a good run.
